Package fr.sorbonne_u.components.pubsub.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Observer
    A class can implement the Observer interface when it wants to be informed of changes in observable objects.
    Observer.Offered
    An Offered interface
    Observer.Required
    A Required interface
    PublisherService
    The PublisherService interface defines the contract that a Publisher Component must uphold.
    PublisherService.Required
    A required interface
    PubSubService
    The PubsubService interface defines the contract that a PubSub Component must uphold.
    PubSubService.Offered
    An offered interface
    SubscriberService
    The SubscriberService interface defines the contract that a Subscriber Component must uphold.
    SubscriberService.Required
    A required interface
    Subscription
    The PubSub must keep track of the subscribers that it needs to notify at each publication, hence the Subscription interface is just an abstraction of a subscriber.
